2025 PMSL CSA Fall Season ko Official Broadcast ma swagat cha ‚Äì Grand Finals! üëë

It all comes down to this‚Äîthe final battleground jaha legacy haru forge hunchan ra  matra euta team le trophy uthaune cha.

üî• Chaos. Clutch. History. Sab huncha.
Yehi ho moment jasko lagi pura region wait gardai thiyo‚Äîwho will rise as the PMSL CSA Fall Champion of 2025? üèÜ

Today, the SMASH RULE takes over:

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£ At the end of Day 2, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Today is the day! Once a team reaches or exceeds the Match Point threshold, they must win a Chicken Dinner in a subsequent match to be crowned champions
3Ô∏è‚É£ Be the Champions! ‚Äì If no team meets both conditions by the end of all 18 matches, the team with the highest total points will be declared the champion.

Everything is on the line ‚ÄîTrophy, legacy, and one final zone.

üí∞Total Prize Pool: $200,000

snippet.description:
It‚Äôs here. It‚Äôs fierce.
The wait is over ‚Äî the Dhurandhar Title Track (Jogi) is finally here!
Packed with fierce beats, bold voices, and unstoppable energy ‚Äî this one‚Äôs pure fire. üî•

Releasing on 5th December 2025

Credits: 
Jio Studios Presents
A B62 Studios Production

An Aditya Dhar Film
DHURANDHAR

Written, Directed and Produced by: Aditya Dhar
Produced by: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced by: Lokesh Dhar

Cast: Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna | R. Madhavan | Arjun Rampal | Sara Arjun

Audio Credits:
Original Song Name: Na De Dil Pardesi Nu (Jogi)
Song name: Dhurandhar - Title Track 
Music: Shashwat Sachdev, Charanjit Ahuja
Produced and Arranged: Shashwat Sachdev
Singers: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Sudhir Yaduvanshi, Shashwat Sachdev, Mohd. Sadiq, Ranjit Kaur
Lyrics: Hanumankind, Jasmine Sandlas, Babu Singh Maan
Music Video: Jayesh Shikarkhane & Team
Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge 
Assistant engineers: Jazbaat, Sohamm, Suryansh
HanumanKind vocals mixed by Akash Shravan

Lyrics:

Ladies and Gentlemen 
You are not ready for this 

Na de dil pardesi nu tainu nit da roona pai jau ga 
Na de dil pardesi nu tainu nit da roona pai jau ga

snippet.title: Arijit Singh - Aaj Se Teri | Akshay Kumar & Radhika Apte | Amit Trivedi | Padman | Lyrical
snippet.description:
Song - Aaj Se Teri
Singer - Arijit Singh
Music - Amit Trivedi
Lyricist - Kausar Munir

Lyrics:
Mukhda -
Aaj Se Teri Saari Galiyaan Meri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Mera Ghar Tera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Teri Saari Galiyaan Meri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Mera Ghar Tera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶
Aaj Se Meri Saari Khushiyaan Teri Ho Gayi,
Aaj Se Tera Gum Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tera Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se Tera Ho Gaya. 

Antara 1- 
Tere Maathe Aaaaa‚Ä¶.Tere Maathe Ke Kumkum Ko
Main Tilak Lagaa Ke Ghoomoonga, 
Teri Baali Ki Chhunchhun Ko
Main Dil Se Lagaa Ke Jhoomoonga‚Ä¶

Meri Chhoti Si Bhoolon, 
Ko Tu Nadiya Mein Baha Dena.
Tere Jude Ke Phoolon Ko, 
Main Apne Shirt Mein Pehnoonga.

Bas Mere Liye Tu Maalpue Kabhi Kabhi Bana Dena‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Meri Saari Ratiyaan Teri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Tera Din Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tera Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se Tera Ho Gaya. 

Antara 2-
Tu Maange Sardi Mein Amiya, 
Jo Maange Garmi Mein Mungphaliyaan, 
Tu Baarish Mein Agar Keh De,
Ja Mere Liye Tu Dhoop Khila.

Toh Main Sooraj‚Ä¶‚Ä¶. Toh Main Sooraj Ko Jhatak Doonga, 
Toh Main Saawan Ko Gatak Loonga,
Toh Saare Taaron Sang Chanda
Main Teri Goad Mein Rakh Doonga-

Bas Mere Liye Tu Khil Ke Kabhi Muskuraa Dena‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Meri Saari Sadiyaan Teri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Tera Pal Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tere Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwaabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se ‚Ä¶‚Ä¶Tera Ho Gaya.

Laxmi Aarti in Hindi,lakshmi aarti,maha lakshmi aarti,‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Ü‡§∞‡§§‡•Ä ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶‡•Ä,‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Ü‡§∞‡§§‡•Ä ‡§π‡§ø‡§Ç‡§¶‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•á‡§Ç,Om Jai Laxmi Mata,om jai lakshmi mata,jai lakshmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata,‡§ú‡§Ø ‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§§‡§æ,‡•ê ‡§ú‡§Ø ‡§≤‡§ï‡•ç‡§∑‡•ç‡§Æ‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡§æ‡§§‡§æ,mahalaxmi songs,om jai laxmi mata,laxmi aarti,laxmi ji ki aarti,lakshmi mata ki aarti,lakshmi ji ki aarti,aarti lakshmi ji ki,aarti laxmi ji ki,laxmi mata ki aarti,laxmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata aarti,maa laxmi aarti,aarti lakshmi mata ki

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

snippet.description:
You‚Äôve seen them dance, you‚Äôve seen them fall in love, now witness the heartbreak when love gets intertwined! Presenting ‚ÄòTumse Behtar‚Äô from ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and written by Manoj Muntashir, this beautiful song is sung by Arijit Singh.

#TumseBehtar #ArijitSingh #TanishkBagchi #SSKTK

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singh‚Äôs Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:
Tumhara-mera milna likha to hoga kahin
Naseebon ka sitara, mila to hoga Kahin

Na Jane kyun ae humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Raaton me, bina tumhare ghabrayein, ghabraayein
Khwaabon me, milo agar khush ho jaayein ho jaayein

Chain ho tum aaram ho shayad
Koi sukoon ki shaam ho shayad
Khushi kahoon ya dil ki tasalli
Kya tumhein doon main naam

Kitabein dekhi saari, mili na koi shaayri
Tareefein karoon kaise, yahi hai muhskil meri

Na Jane kyun a humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi
Jo daraeyin wo hawayein gham ki, tham jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Dekho na ye kamaal hua hai
Aesa dil ka haal hua hai
Dil mera tere itar me dooba
Jaise koi roomal hua hai

Aesi hai khwahish dil me mere
Jaane mujhe sab naam se tere
Aesi diwangi pahle nahin thee
Haal ye pichhle saal hua hai

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Koi nahin tumse behtar, tumse pyaara
Tumse zyaada mera koi nahin!

Leaders afno ground hold garna fight garchan ra challengers afno comeback suru garna tesaile Battleground ajhai fierce huncha.

üî• With the trophy inching closer, tension rises‚ÄîHarek squad lai tha cha ki one mistake could cost them the title .

Aja ko pressure chahi different cha: kura leaderboard climb garne matra haina ‚Äî  leader banne ra match point define garne ko sawal cha. Kinaki bholi, SMASH RULE live hunecha, ra sabai vanda smart ra dominant teams le matra afno terms ma yo game end garne mauka paunechan.

One more day to set the stage. One more chance to secure that chicken dinner. The race to the crown is on.

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£Aja ko dina sakida, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
